FBIS4-57335 "drlat096_j_94005" FBIS-LAT-94-096 Daily Report 17 May 1994 Panama Government Transition Team Formed, Ministers-Designate Named Government Transition Team Formed, Ministers-Designate Named Ministers-Designate Namelist PA1705235294 Panama City Telemetro Television Network in Spanish 1730 GMT 17 May 94 PA1705235294 Panama City Telemetro Television Network Spanish BFN [From the "Telemetro Reports" newscast] [Text] President-elect Ernesto Perez Balladares today announced in Santiago de Veraguas the appointment of the new government and justice minister. With this appointment and those announced earlier, the cabinet of Perez Balladares will be as follows: ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Raul Montenegro |Government and Justice Minister | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Luis Blanco |Public Works Minister | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Aida de Rivera |Health Minister | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Nitzia de Villarreal |Commerce and Industries Minister | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Raul Arango |Presidency Minister | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Olmedo Miranda, Jr. |Finance and Treasury Minister | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Guillermo Chapman |Planning and Economic Policy Minister | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Francisco Sanchez Cardenas |Housing Minister | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Mitchel Doens |Labor and Social Welfare Minister | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Gabriel Lewis Galindo |Foreign Relations Minister | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Carlos Souza Lennox |Agricultural Development Minister | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
